    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8 engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced. The chassis retains its factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and shows zero signs of subframe fatigue. Presented in Alpine White with a carbon fiber roof, the paint depth and panel gaps are within original tolerances. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
